headline: UBS Raises SBA Communications (SBAC) Price Target to $285, Keeps “Buy”
summary: SBA Communications Corporation (NASDAQ:SBAC) is one of Goldman Sachs’ top REIT stock picks. On July 8, 2025, UBS analyst Batya Levi reiterated a “Buy” rating on SBA Communications (NASDAQ:SBAC), signaling continued confidence in the company’s performance and growth outlook.
